091EA8DD.Line13.6D03F: Had that been her goal all along?

27FCB7D0.Line7.6D03F: Bound as one against the encroaching darkness, like the Horadrim of old.

3D079BE1.Line17.6D03F: And Elias, the damn fool, was too blind to see it.

5A1F4B4A.Line1.6D03F: I wonder what old Deckard Cain would have written in his chronicles if he had seen us.

5B6C043C.Line21.6D03F: We were the world’s only hope.

6F2A2F5B.Line11.6D03F: One thing was certain, at least: Lilith meant to devour Mephisto and claim his power as her own.

8E083E4E.Line5.6D03F: Two old friends reunited. New allies eager to learn from our vast knowledge.

A313225F.Line15.6D03F: Not Sanctuary, but a bid to reign in Hell?

C1F13152.Line9.6D03F: They were probably lost and bitter just like us, but Cain had a gift for seeing the good in people.

D6FC1563.Line19.6D03F: Perhaps we weren’t perfect, but we knew we had to make a stand.
